Messages
========

Externalizes strings. You can group messages by context. You can also
use variable substitution.

Create a messages.yml file under <app>/config/messages.yml

Examples
========

Messages["books/rails"]                  # => "I'm a Rails book"
Messages.get("books/mysterious", "good") # => "I'm a good book" (if mysterious is "I'm a {0} book")


